{
  "page": "Feature quote/92",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Bring us <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor</a>’s head, and I know His Grace will be most grateful. <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Joffrey\">Joff</a> may have liked the man, but <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tommen\">Tommen</a> was always afraid of him... with good reason it would seem.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a><br />“When a dog goes bad, the fault lies with his master.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_12\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 12\">Chapter 12</a>, Cersei III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403175720\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 56/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 309/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.971      1 -total\n100.00%    3.971      1 Te